*vala-common-0.18.0 (25 Sep 2012)

  25 Sep 2012; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  -vala-common-0.17.6.ebuild, -vala-common-0.17.7.ebuild,
  +vala-common-0.18.0.ebuild:
  Bump to vala-0.18 stable; drop pre-releases.

*vala-common-0.17.7 (22 Sep 2012)

  22 Sep 2012; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> +vala-common-0.17.7.ebuild,
  -vala-common-0.17.5.ebuild:
  Version bump, drop old.

  13 Sep 2012; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> vala-common-0.17.6.ebuild:
  Marked ~x64-macos

*vala-common-0.17.6 (05 Sep 2012)

  05 Sep 2012; Nirbheek Chauhan <nirbheek@gentoo.org>
  +vala-common-0.17.6.ebuild:
  Bump; bug fixes and binding updates

*vala-common-0.17.5 (20 Aug 2012)

  20 Aug 2012; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  +vala-common-0.17.5.ebuild, +metadata.xml:
  Split out dev-lang/vala's aclocal macros and makefile templates into a
  separate package to make it possible to autoreconf packages with an optional
  vala dependency without installing all of dev-lang/vala.
